title: 399: What To Do If My Manifestation Is Not Working with Sahara Rose
itunes:title: 399: What To Do If My Manifestation Is Not Working with Sahara Rose
description:
You set your manifestation on the moon, you meditated on it, did all the things but it’s still not happening. What’s up?! In this episode I share WHY and HOW to overcome it.. Or if/ when you even need to. I share my own story of NOT manifesting my “dream” condo and how it was a blessing and how REJECTION is sometimes REDIRECTION. Enjoy!

Create a thriving career as a Certified Soul Purpose Coach at Dharma Coaching Institute. Learn more: www.dharmacoachinginstitute.com

Join Rose Gold Goddesses, the sacred sisterhood collective all about embodying the Goddess within at www.RoseGoldGoddesses.com
